 <channel>pecl.php.net</channel>
 <summary>PHP extension for OpenZFS on FreeBSD</summary>
 <description>
  This extension provides PHP interface to OpenZFS on FreeBSD systems.
  It allows PHP applications to interact with ZFS pools and datasets
  through the libzfs and libzfs_core libraries.
  
  Currently supports:
  - zfs_list(): List all ZFS datasets with properties
  - zpool_list(): List all ZFS pools with status and properties
 </description>
